    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, she\u2019s been a total gem. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has clearly been well-loved over the years\u2014perfect for someone who wants a dependable, smooth drive without any fuss. It\u2019s ready for its next adventure, so come take a look and see for yourself! Feel free to message me with any questions!",
