    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained 2004 BMW M3 (E46), a true icon of analog performance. Under the hood lies the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine, featuring individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS system for a linear power band up to its 8,000 RPM redline. This example features the sought-after 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox and a factory-spec limited-slip differential for superior corner-exit traction. Recent preventative maintenance includes subframe reinforcement and a comprehensive VANOS overhaul, ensuring the chassis and valvetrain are robust. The suspension has been enhanced with Bilstein dampers for improved damping rates without sacrificing street compliance. This is a mechanically sound, driver-focused machine ready for the twisties.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 11
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "2019 SUV. Good condition. Well-maintained engine. Clean interior. New tires installed last month. No accidents. Title in hand.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
