    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a standout example of pride in ownership, offering a harmonious blend of performance and comfort. The exterior maintains a brilliant shine, showing only the light, expected character of a well-loved car that has been parked mostly in a garage. Inside, you\u2019ll find a pristine, non-smoking environment where the premium materials have been preserved with care; the seats are supportive and free of significant wear, and all onboard technology\u2014from the infotainment system to the climate control\u2014operates flawlessly. Under the hood, the engine runs quiet and strong, a testament to a rigorous preventative maintenance schedule. It has recently undergone a full inspection and fluid service, with the tires and brakes showing plenty of life for the miles ahead. This car delivers a smooth, confident ride that feels as reliable today as it did when it first hit the road. It is a complete package for a discerning buyer looking for a high-quality daily driver.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 11
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presented for your consideration is a distinguished example of automotive excellence, meticulously maintained to ensure continued peak performance. This vehicle exhibits a refined aesthetic and robust mechanical integrity, representing a superior choice for the discerning driver. Every aspect of this automobile has been evaluated to confirm its adherence to our high standards of roadworthiness and comfort. For those seeking a well-preserved asset that offers a seamless synthesis of luxury and dependability, this offering stands as a testament to quality craftsmanship.",
