    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and she\u2019s been such a reliable companion. It\u2019s in solid shape and runs like a dream\u2014perfect for someone who wants a dependable car without the brand-new price tag. It's been well-cared for and is totally ready for its next adventure with you! Feel free to reach out if you have any questions or want to come take it for a spin!",
