      "description": "This E46 M3 is a mechanically sound example featuring the high-revving S54B32 inline-six, equipped with individual throttle bodies and high-pressure double VANOS for peak volumetric efficiency. Power is delivered via a sought-after Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission and a 3.64 ratio limited-slip differential. The chassis has been addressed with rear subframe reinforcement and upgraded polyurethane bushings to maintain structural rigidity under lateral load. Featuring a responsive throttle map and a true 8,000 RPM redline, this M3 offers an analog driving experience with the precise turn-in and balanced kinematics the chassis is renowned for.",
